summary: With a 20 year background in competitive sports, I am currently working in the fitness industry. Ranging from customer service to athletic clothing design, I am also managing two social media business accounts. I am constantly creating content and using creative skills to invite consumers and raise revenue. My creativity translates also to clothing design where I use Adobe Illustrator and Alibaba to custom design Athleisure. My current goal is to create an entire line of athleisure wear for Men in the health and wellness industry.
